Privacy Policy
Last Updated: 03/17/2021
Next Drop is not interested in collecting or obtaining any of your personal data.
There may be non-personally identifiable data that is collected to help support and track the features used in Next Drop. This data is made available to Next Drop in an anonymous fashion.
Personally-Identifiable Information
Next Drop does not gather or transmit any Personally-Identifiable Information.
